header.gameNote: SHAMROCK OFFICE SOLUTIONS CLASSIC AT MORAGA CA

article.headline: Stephen F.Austin 73, Howard 50
article.story: MORAGA, Calif. -- Eddie Williams had 17 points and eight rebounds, Jereal Scott added 14 points and Stephen F. Austin beat Howard 73-50 in the Shamrock Office Solutions Classic on Tuesday night. Will Reinke added 11 points for the Lumberjacks (8-3), who committed just five turnovers while winning for the seventh time in eight games. The lone blemish in the streak was a 72-69 loss at Arkansas on Dec. 19. Calvin Thompson scored 16 points and was the only Howard player in double figures. The Bison (1-11) shot just 35.6 percent and grabbed only seven offensive rebounds.
